		<tr>
			<td colspan="6" class="DetailTitle" style="text-align:center;">
                            Summary on Grant Application Form</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="6" class="DetailValue" style="padding:5px;">
                        <span id="lblAbstract">This project is an experimental study of chemical scale inhibitor for application in HP/HT reservoirs.  Equipment (2 cells) will be designed and built to test inhibitors for inhibition efficiency, calcium capability, through stability and bulk adsorption at HP/HT conditions (200c and 15,000 psi).  An assessment of some mineralogical aspects of formation damage will also be made in the adsorption measurements.  Results will be used to make a series of recomendations on scale inhibitor selection and improvement to both the oil industry and , more importantly, the chemical supply industry who serve them.</span>
                        </td>
		</tr>
